1. InputMismatchException

Wrong input type (letters instead of numbers).

2. ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException

If a loop or index goes outside the array.

3. NullPointerException

When you try to access a null product slot.

4. IllegalArgumentException

Negative price, negative quantity, empty name, or invalid expiration date.

5. ProductNotFoundException (custom)

Thrown when update/delete/search fails because the ID does not exist.

6. InventoryFullException (custom)

Thrown when trying to add a product but the array is full.
